summary: AN Ordinance accepting electrical overhead distribution easements over portions of Homecroft; Gilman's Addition to The City of Seattle; Fischer's Highway Garden Tracts; southeast 1/4 of Section 12, Township 23 North, Range 3 East; Dewey's Addition to The City of Seattle; Northwest 1/4 of Section 1, Township 26 North, Range 3 East; and McKenny's Addition to Seattle, as described below and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
